<br>
The spell Phantasmal Armor dropped. It's level 54, and is pretty much the exact same spell as Phantom Armor (52). Gives the exact same AC, gives back 5 extra HP a tick (for 8 total) and does not appear to give back any mana at all. <br>
<br>
The difference is the mana cost - 225 vs 400 I think? and the spell component cost - 4 cats eye vs 1 pearl.<br>
<br>
Clearly this spell is bugged. I have submitted comments to Verant. I have no idea if this spell is supposed to be Transons Phantasmal Protection or not, but I would assume so since I can't find any reference to it at all.<br>
<br>
Sharlis~<br>
